    { "id":"c-12-primary-universes","text":"The 12 Primary Universes constitute MAATAA OS","status":"PARTIAL","blockedReason":"All 12 are extracted as their own .hkd files (this corpus). They exist as boards/visions. Only Lipi & Script, Education (via lipi-runtime), and Knowledge (via kbs-runtime) have partial implementation substrate.","sourceImage":"user-provided/2026-05-28/master-meta-map-board.png","sourceSectionId":"sec-12-universes","confidence":0.90 },
    { "id":"c-7-universal-chains","text":"7 Universal Chains (Identity/Knowledge/Value/Execution/Verification/Distribution/Impact) connect everything","status":"UNVERIFIED","blockedReason":"Architectural concept. Identity Chain = runtime-hkd-registry scaffold. Knowledge Chain = kbs-graph. Verification Chain = runtime-validation scaffold + governed-production-gate. Others have no current owner.","sourceImage":"user-provided/2026-05-28/master-meta-map-board.png","sourceSectionId":"sec-7-chains","confidence":0.85 },
    { "id":"c-5-dharmic-pillars","text":"5 Dharmic Pillars: Satya / Ahimsa / Seva / Samatvam / Swaraj","status":"UNVERIFIED","blockedReason":"Foundational ethical principles. Not a software claim.","sourceImage":"user-provided/2026-05-28/master-meta-map-board.png","sourceSectionId":"sec-5-pillars","confidence":0.90 },
    { "id":"c-cross-universe-integration","text":"Cross-Universe Integration Layer: Data Interoperability / Semantic Layer / Identity & Access / Orchestration / Security & Trust / Audit & Transparency","status":"UNVERIFIED","blockedReason":"Six architectural concerns. Closest existing substrate: kbs-graph (semantic), evidence-generate.mjs (audit). Orchestration + security do not yet exist.","sourceImage":"user-provided/2026-05-28/master-meta-map-board.png","sourceSectionId":"sec-integration-layer","confidence":0.85 },
